  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHAT IS RAINWIDGET</h2>RainWidget is a powerful widget engine based on Chrome Core that allow you create stunning smooth animations widgets using the latest web technologies(JS HTML5 CSS3) for your desktop . Choose an existing widget or create your own and share it to the Online Gallery!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Make your desktop lively with stunning smooth animation widgets.<br></li><li>Download widgets via the built-in online gallery with just one-click.<br></li><li>Clean UI, Easy to use and don't use too much resource<br></li><li>Support create widgets with latest Web technology(JS HTML5 CSS3 ).<br></li><li>Use the online gallery to share your widgets.<br></li><li>Support Steam Cloud Sync Widgets and User Data</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/983820/extras/78f53e69508a1e6acf7a048011af95f6.poster.avif?t=1577013219\" width=416 height=504 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/983820/extras/78f53e69508a1e6acf7a048011af95f6.webm?t=1577013219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/983820/extras/78f53e69508a1e6acf7a048011af95f6.mp4?t=1577013219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/983820/extras/9b0fbb07266ba1ee2ac2ba4e58c44072.poster.avif?t=1577013219\" width=652 height=520 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/983820/extras/9b0fbb07266ba1ee2ac2ba4e58c44072.webm?t=1577013219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/983820/extras/9b0fbb07266ba1ee2ac2ba4e